---
title: Classic Beef, Venison & Beetroot Relish Burger with Smokey Aioli & Herby Kumara Fries
description: We've packed almighty flavour into these beef and venison patties with the crowd-pleasing Nan's special seasoning. Top them with smokey
aioli and mixed leaves, then add an easy beetroot relish for a fun kick.
